Module camp_management_and_application_system
Package model.camp

Class Enquiry

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.camp.Enquiry
  • public class Enquiry
extends java.lang.Object
    This Enquiry Class represent inquiry related to a camp. An inquiry is sent in by a student and the student may then recieve replies from staff or committee members of the camp.
